snippet.title: Let's Play Downfall To The Turnabout Part 1: We Need A Break
snippet.description:
It is only half the prologue, but we need something short to break up the rest of DeSu 2! This fan game will be epic once it is finished, I promise!
Game made by DudeWithAMask of the Court Records forums!
